---
title: Pesto Bocconcini and Chicken Flatbread Pizzas with Mixed Green Salad
description: Rich basil pesto, tender bell peppers, juicy chicken and creamy, melt-in-your-mouth bocconcini top these quick and easy naan pizzas! A sprinkle of chili flakes adds a spicy kick, if desired. Mix in bites of the fresh salad for a delightful dinner.
